<i> at the Vienna.</i>

35:02.134 --> 35:03.834
- Wow.
- Oh-ho.

35:03.869 --> 35:05.635
- Wow.
- That is amazing.

35:05.671 --> 35:07.737
Holy smokes.

35:07.773 --> 35:11.808
- This is beautiful.
- This is incredible.

35:11.844 --> 35:13.176
Bravo.

