35:52.751 --> 35:54.784
<i> (Gordon)</i>
<i> I could see that everyone</i>
<i> was thrilled</i>

35:54.820 --> 35:56.086
<i>with the changes at the Vienna.</i>

35:56.121 --> 35:58.121
Good.
