36:14.006 --> 36:16.973
<i> (Gordon)</i>
<i> And right now I'm worried</i>
<i> where Lisa's head is,</i>

36:17.009 --> 36:19.776
<i> going into relaunch</i>
<i> this evening.</i>

36:19.811 --> 36:26.383
<i> ¶ ¶</i>

36:26.418 --> 36:28.618
Good evening!

