to sound ungrateful.

40:35.100 --> 40:37.200
Oh, I'm not ungrateful.
I am just so shocked--

40:37.235 --> 40:41.037
From the new management system
to Dave--

40:41.072 --> 40:42.639
I'm coming across wrong

40:42.674 --> 40:44.407
if you think
that I'm being ungrateful,

40:44.443 --> 40:45.742
'cause I'm really not.

40:45.777 --> 40:47.444
It sounds like that.

40:47.479 --> 40:49.379
No.
Not at all.

40:49.414 --> 40:51.080
I can't come in
and wave a magic wand

40:51.116 --> 40:53.483
and transform 15 bedrooms
and put a brand-new kitchen.

40:53.518 --> 40:55.285
You now know
what needs to happen.

40:55.320 --> 40:57.153
I do.

40:57.189 --> 40:59.422
But I need to tell you something
that you're not gonna like.

40:59.458 --> 41:02.358
- I arranged for a new stove...
- You did?

41:02.394 --> 41:04.194
To come,

41:04.229 --> 41:07.397
and then when I got the engineer
to come and survey the place,

41:07.432 --> 41:09.466
unfortunately,
he had to leave,

41:09.501 --> 41:11.701
because he was gonna shut
the place down,

41:11.736 --> 41:14.337
'cause there's practices
that are taking place in there

41:14.372 --> 41:15.672
that aren't appropriate.

41:15.707 --> 41:17.240
You're saying
the gas systems--

41:17.275 --> 41:18.741
The whole setup
underneath there.

41:18.777 --> 41:21.277
Nothing's been changed
in 13 years.

41:21.313 --> 41:24.581
And it's on the verge of
running illegally.

41:24.616 --> 41:27.217
- Okay.
- Mm-hmm.

41:27.252 --> 41:29.152
Listen, I came here to help,

41:29.187 --> 41:32.055
but you need to help yourselves
and dig deep

41:32.090 --> 41:34.791
and stick together, okay?

41:34.826 --> 41:36.593
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

41:36.628 --> 41:38.228
- Good luck.
- Okay.

41:38.263 --> 41:39.729
- Thank you, Gordon.
- Okay.

41:39.764 --> 41:42.665
- Good night.
- Thank you.

41:42.701 --> 41:44.467
-<i> Auf wiedersehen. </i>
- Safe traveling.

41:44.503 --> 41:45.635
[exhales deeply]

41:45.670 --> 41:48.605
Man, that's hard work.

41:48.640 --> 41:51.608
<i> [dramatic music]</i>

41:51.643 --> 41:54.644
<i> ¶ ¶</i>

41:54.679 --> 41:56.179
<i> [upbeat music]</i>

41:56.214 --> 41:57.747
<i> (Gordon)</i>
<i> Soon after I left,</i>

41:57.782 --> 42:00.450
<i> Lisa and Jonathan reverted</i>
<i> to the old Vienna...</i>

42:00.485 --> 42:03.186
(Lisa)
This is something
that belongs here.

42:03.221 --> 42:04.687
That came with the house.

42:04.723 --> 42:07.524
What are you doing?
