42:12.931 --> 42:14.597
<i> (Gordon)</i>
<i> They chose</i>
<i> not to take my advice</i>

42:14.633 --> 42:16.666
<i> about running the inn</i>
<i> properly...</i>

42:16.701 --> 42:18.401
