Listen to me about what should
be going on in the kitchen.

42:18.436 --> 42:20.103
<i> (Gordon)</i>
<i> And as a result,</i>

42:20.138 --> 42:22.639
<i> their reputation in town</i>
<i> remains the same.</i>
